{"thag2.38:0.1":"Theragatha 2.38 ","thag2.38:0.2":"Dukanipata ","thag2.38:0.3":"Catutthavagga ","thag2.38:0.4":"Nisabhattheragatha ","thag2.38:1.1":"“Panca kamagune hitva, ","thag2.38:1.2":"Piyarupe manorame; ","thag2.38:1.3":"Saddhaya ghara nikkhamma, ","thag2.38:1.4":"Dukkhassantakaro bhave. ","thag2.38:2.1":"Nabhinandami maranam, ","thag2.38:2.2":"nabhinandami jivitam; ","thag2.38:2.3":"Kalanca patikankhami, ","thag2.38:2.4":"sampajano patissato”ti. ","thag2.38:2.5":"… Nisabho thero …. "}